Description: Native Linux control & casting app for Epson projectors
 The ultimate, enterprise-grade controller for your Epson projectors.
 Take complete command over network and mDNS projection. Features advanced diagnostic tools,
 custom alias management, direct ESC/VP console access, and native PipeWire screen casting.
